<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" data-theme="{{ output_theme|default('dark') }}">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>{{ report.title }}</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: dark;
      --bg: #0d1020;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      --panel-strong: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      --text: #f7f7fb;
      --muted: #a8b0c7;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      --accent: #8b5cf6;
      --accent-2: #22d3ee;
      --good: #34d399;
    }
    [data-theme="light"], [data-theme="newsroom-white"] {
      color-scheme: light;
      --bg: #f6f7fb;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,.82);
      --panel-strong: #ffffff;
      --text: #111827;
      --muted: #5b6477;
      --line: rgba(17,24,39,.12);
      --accent: #6d28d9;
      --accent-2: #0891b2;
      --good: #047857;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(139,92,246,.24), transparent 34rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 10%, rgba(34,211,238,.18), transparent 30rem),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Pretendard", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.68;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 60%, transparent); }
    .wrap { width: min(1060px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; padding: 52px 0 72px; }
    .hero {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--panel-strong), var(--panel));
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 44px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h1 { margin: 18px 0 12px; font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 68px); line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: -.06em; }
    .hero-summary { max-width: 820px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px; }
    .metrics, .keyword-row, .card-grid { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .metrics {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: nowrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 26px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .metric, .brief-card, .section-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--panel);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .metric {
      display: inline-flex;
      flex: 1 0 auto;
      align-items: baseline;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 7px;
      min-width: 0;
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .metric strong { display: inline; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1; }
    .metric span, .muted { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
    .section-card { margin-top: 18px; padding: clamp(18px, 3vw, 30px); }
    .section-head { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .section-index {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: white;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    h2 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 34px); line-height: 1.22; letter-spacing: -.03em; }
    h3 { margin: 34px 0 12px; font-size: 18px; }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--line); margin: 20px 0; }
    .image-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin: 18px 0; }
    figure { margin: 0; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 18px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    figure img { display: block; width: 100%; max-height: 420px; object-fit: cover; }
    figcaption { padding: 9px 12px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    li { margin: 8px 0; }
    blockquote {
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-2);
      padding: 10px 0 10px 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(34,211,238,.08), transparent);
    }
    .tag-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 14px; }
    .tag {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 3px 9px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .source-list { display: grid; gap: 8px; padding-left: 0; list-style: none; }
    .source-list li { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .source-list a { color: var(--text); }
    .brief-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-top: 28px; }
    .brief-card h2 { font-size: 22px; }
    footer { margin-top: 36px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .brief-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section-head { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">Signal Briefing · {{ report.report_date }}</span>
      <h1>{{ report.title }}</h1>
      <p class="hero-summary">{{ report.summary_ko }}</p>
      <div class="metrics" aria-label="report metrics">
        <div class="metric"><strong>{{ report.stats.total_sources|default(0) }}</strong><span>수집 항목</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>{{ report.stats.ai_relevant|default(0) }}</strong><span>AI 관련</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>{{ report.stats.clusters|default(sections|length) }}</strong><span>최종 섹션</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>{{ report.stats.verified|default(0) }}</strong><span>검증 신호</span></div>
      </div>
      {% if report.stats.main_event %}
      <blockquote><strong>메인 이벤트</strong> — {{ report.stats.main_event }}</blockquote>
      {% endif %}
      {% if report.stats.top_keywords %}
      <div class="tag-row" aria-label="top keywords">
        {% for keyword in report.stats.top_keywords[:8] %}
        <span class="tag">#{{ keyword }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% if report.stats.signal_axes %}
      <p class="muted">신호 축: {{ report.stats.signal_axes|join(" · ") }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </section>

    {% if sections %}
      {% for section in sections %}
      <article class="section-card">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="section-index">{{ loop.index }}</span>
          <div>
            <h2>{{ section.title or section.title_ko }}</h2>
            <p class="muted">{{ section.category|default("signal") }} · score {{ "%.2f"|format(section.importance_score|default(0)) }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>
        {% if section.fact_summary %}
        <p>{{ section.fact_summary }}</p>
        {% elif section.summary_ko %}
        <p>{{ section.summary_ko }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% set image_url = (section.content_image_urls[0] if section.content_image_urls else section.og_image_url) %}
        {% if image_url %}
        <div class="image-grid">
          <figure>
            <img src="{{ image_url }}" alt="{{ section.title or section.title_ko }}">
            <figcaption>대표 이미지 · 원문 출처 기준</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if section.image_detail_hint %}
        <p><strong>이미지에서 확인된 디테일 —</strong> {{ section.image_detail_hint }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if section.key_updates %}
        <h3>주요 소식들</h3>
        <ul>
          {% for update in section.key_updates[:4] %}
          <li>{{ update }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        {% if section.social_signal_summary %}
        <blockquote><strong>소셜 신호</strong> — {{ section.social_signal_summary }}</blockquote>
        {% endif %}
        {% if section.inference_summary %}
        <blockquote><strong>시사점</strong> — {{ section.inference_summary }}</blockquote>
        {% endif %}

        {% if section.sources_json %}
        <h3>주요 출처</h3>
        <ul class="source-list">
          {% for src in section.sources_json[:5] %}
          <li>↳ <a href="{{ src.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ src.name or src.source_name or src.url }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        {% if section.tags %}
        <div class="tag-row">
          {% for tag in section.tags[:8] %}
          <span class="tag">#{{ tag }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <article class="section-card">
        <h2>오늘 수집된 기사로 만들 섹션이 없습니다</h2>
        <p class="muted">수집원, 날짜 범위, LLM 프록시 상태를 확인한 뒤 다시 생성하세요.</p>
      </article>
    {% endif %}

    <section class="brief-grid">
      <div class="brief-card">
        <h2>📊 오늘의 온도</h2>
        <ul>
          {% for item in report.stats.today_temperature|default([]) %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% else %}
          <li>섹션별 검증 신호와 소셜 반응을 함께 확인하세요.</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="brief-card">
        <h2>💡 행동으로 옮길 것</h2>
        <ul>
          {% for item in report.stats.action_items|default([]) %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% else %}
          <li>관심 있는 항목은 원문 링크를 열어 릴리스 노트와 제한 사항을 확인하세요.</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      Generated at {{ report.created_at }} · output_style={{ output_style }} · theme={{ output_theme|default('dark') }}
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
